## Questions About Licensing?

- **For code licensing**: Open an issue on GitHub or check the MIT License FAQ
- **For content licensing**: See https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/ or contact us
- **General questions**: Email: legal@shriramjourney.com

---

## Open Source & Dharma Philosophy

This licensing reflects our commitment to the Dharma principle of **Gyaan Daan** (sharing knowledge).

- Code is shared freely for innovation (MIT)
- Content is shared with community protection (CC-BY-SA)
- Together, we preserve and advance the Ramayana legacy

